'''帕特里克·羅伯茨'''（{{lang-en|Patrick Roberts}}；{{bd|1997年|2月5日}}）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]足球運動員。在場上的位置是二前鋒或右邊鋒。現在效力英格蘭球隊[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|桑德兰]]。

==球會生涯==
羅伯茨在13歲時從[[AFC溫布頓|AFC溫布頓]]轉會至[[富勒姆足球俱樂部|富勒姆]]<ref name="contract reaction">{{cite web|url=http://www.fulhamfc.com/news/2014/february/14/roberts-deal-delight |title=Roberts deal delight |publisher=Fulham Official Website |accessdate=8 May 2014 |date=14 February 2014 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140503164907/http://www.fulhamfc.com/news/2014/february/14/roberts-deal-delight |archivedate=2014-05-03|deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The star makers: How Fulham became one of the best youth academies in the modern game |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/news-and-comment/the-star-makers-how-fulham-became-one-of-the-best-youth-academies-in-the-modern-game-9291146.html |website={{url|http://independent.co.uk/|publisher=independent.co.uk}} |accessdate=19 August 2014 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819133054/http://www.independent.co.uk/sport/football/news-and-comment/the-star-makers-how-fulham-became-one-of-the-best-youth-academies-in-the-modern-game-9291146.html |archivedate=2014-08-19|deadurl=yes }}</ref>，17歲生日後便簽下職業合約，為期兩年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fulhamfc.com/news/2014/february/06/roberts-pro-deal |title=Roberts' Pro Deal |publisher=Fulham Official Websure |accessdate=8 May 2014 |date=6 February 2014 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140503164325/http://www.fulhamfc.com/news/2014/february/06/roberts-pro-deal |archivedate=2014-05-03|deadurl=no }}</ref>。羅伯茨描述簽下職業合約是他「人生中最棒的感覺之一」<ref name="contract reaction" />。

2014年3月15日對[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|纽卡斯尔联]]賽事，他入選大軍替補名單<ref name="Newcastle">{{cite web|title=Fulham 1 – 0 Newcastle|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/26493211|publisher=BBC|accessdate=18 March 2014|date=15 March 2014|archive-date=2015-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151105232038/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/26493211|dead-url=no}}</ref>，教練[[菲利斯·馬加夫|菲利斯·馬加夫]]形容他為「天才」<ref>{{cite web|title=Magath: I Hate To Lose|url=http://www.fulhamfc.com/news/2014/march/15/magath-i-hate-to-lose|publisher=Fulham FC|accessdate=18 March 2014|date=15 March 2014|archive-date=2014-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506234837/http://www.fulhamfc.com/news/2014/march/15/magath-i-hate-to-lose|dead-url=no}}</ref>。3月22日對[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]的比賽，他在55分入替上場，完成他英超首秀<ref>{{cite web|title=Man City 5 – 0 Fulham|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/26590071|publisher=BBC|accessdate=22 March 2014|archive-date=2015-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150822145849/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/26590071|dead-url=no}}</ref>。5月5日，羅伯茨在2014年青年足總盃決賽次回合中打進一球，但球隊總比數7-6不敵[[切尔西足球俱乐部|切尔西]]<ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27288435 "FA Youth Cup final: Chelsea beat Fulham 7–6 on aggregate"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27288435 |date=20140509204843 }} BBC Sport. 5 May 2014. Retrieved 6 May 2014.</ref>。

羅伯茨在2014/15賽季首次上場是8月9日揭幕日對[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|伊普斯维奇城]]，上場不久後便交出助攻。2014年8月20日對[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]賽事，他首次以先發身份上場。

===曼城===
2015年7月19日，罗伯茨与曼城签订了一份长期合同，费用未公开，据信约为1200万英镑。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/9917664/patrick-roberts-signs-for-manchester-city-from-fulham |title=Patrick Roberts: Manchester City sign Fulham teenager |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2015-07-19 |access-date=2015-07-19 |language=en |archive-date=2022-01-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121155153/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/9917664/patrick-roberts-signs-for-manchester-city-from-fulham }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Manchester City sign Fulham's Patrick Roberts to swell homegrown contingent|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/jul/19/manchester-city-sign-patrick-roberts-fulham|work=The Guardian|access-date=22 August 2015|date=2015-07-19|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516120541/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/jul/19/manchester-city-sign-patrick-roberts-fulham}}</ref>罗伯茨在[[2015年國際冠軍盃|2015年國際冠軍盃]]季前赛对阵皇家马德里的比赛中替补[[捷西斯·拿華斯|捷西斯·拿華斯]]上场。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Manchester City vs. Real Madrid – 24 July 2015 – Soccerway|url = https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/07/24/world/international-champions-cup/manchester-city-football-club/real-madrid-club-de-futbol/2032770/|website = uk.soccerway.com|access-date = 2015-07-24|language = en|archive-date = 2022-04-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220421014452/https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/07/24/world/international-champions-cup/manchester-city-football-club/real-madrid-club-de-futbol/2032770/}}</ref>2015年9月22日，罗伯茨在联赛杯4-1战胜[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|桑德兰]]的比赛中替补出场，首次代表曼城出场。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/sep/22/sunderland-manchester-city-capital-one-cup-match-report |title=Sunderland 1 – 4 Man City |work=The Guardian |date=2015-09-22 |access-date=2015-09-22 |language=en |archive-date=2022-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220507024038/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2015/sep/22/sunderland-manchester-city-capital-one-cup-match-report }}</ref> 他在以4-1负于托特纳姆热刺的比赛中为曼城完成了他的联赛处子秀，替补[[塞尔希奥·阿奎罗|塞尔希奥·阿奎罗]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title = Tottenham Hotspur vs. Manchester City – 26 September 2015|url = https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/09/26/england/premier-league/tottenham-hotspur-football-club/manchester-city-football-club/2043111|website = uk.soccerway.com|access-date = 2015-09-26|language = en|archive-date = 2022-01-21|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220121155828/https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2015/09/26/england/premier-league/tottenham-hotspur-football-club/manchester-city-football-club/2043111/}}</ref>

====凯尔特人(外借)====
2016年1月29日，据报道，凯尔特人与曼城达成了为期18个月的罗伯茨租借协议，而该球员正在格拉斯哥接受体检。<ref>{{cite news|last=McLaughlin|first=Chris|title=Patrick Roberts: Manchester City midfielder to join Celtic on loan|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35444000|access-date=2016-01-30|work=BBC Sport|date=2016-01-29|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220515084907/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35444000}}</ref>转让于同年2月1日得到确认。<ref>{{cite news |title=Celtic sign Colin Kazim-Richards & Patrick Roberts, send Ciftci on loan |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35459424 |publisher=BBC Sport |date=1 date=2016-02-01 |access-date=2016-02-22 |archive-date=2022-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220517162910/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35459424 }}</ref>几天后，他在凯尔特人U20 4-0战胜马瑟韦尔的比赛中在最后一分钟为凯尔特人U20打进第四球，并为其他三个进球提供助攻。<ref>{{cite news|title=Celtic fans hail Patrick Roberts after impressive debut in youth team victory over Motherwell|url=http://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/celtic-fans-hail-patrick-roberts-7317067#9QqBpUPwrd3mcDMy.97|access-date=2016-04-02|work=Daily Record|date=2016-02-05|language=5n|archive-date=2022-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121155704/https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/celtic-fans-hail-patrick-roberts-7317067#9QqBpUPwrd3mcDMy.97}}</ref>罗伯茨在2016 年2月20日为凯尔特人完成了他的球队处子秀，在凯尔特人公园以 3-0 击败因弗内斯 CT 的比赛的最后几分钟替补出场。<ref name="fb156">{{cite web|title=Games involving Roberts, Patrick in season 2015/2016|url=http://www.fitbastats.com/celtic/player_games.php?playerid=7903|website=FitbaStats|access-date=2016-04-02|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122012509/https://www.fitbastats.com/celtic/player_games.php?playerid=7903}}</ref><ref name="start">{{cite news|last1=Hawkins|first1=Billy|title=Celtic fans react on Twitter to Patrick Roberts' full debut performance|url=http://www.hitc.com/en-gb/2016/03/03/celtic-fans-react-on-twitter-to-patrick-roberts-performance-v-du/|access-date=2016-04-02|work=HITC|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122010942/https://www.hitc.com/en-gb/2016/03/03/celtic-fans-react-on-twitter-to-patrick-roberts-performance-v-du/}}</ref> 他于3月2日在主场对阵邓迪的联赛中首次首发出场。儘管凯尔特人在 0-0 的比數只能得到一場平局，但罗伯茨被认为看起来“敏锐”并显示出“他的天赋闪光”。<ref name="start" />

2016年4月2日，罗伯茨打进了他在凯尔特人正式比賽中的第一個进球，在凯尔特人队以3-1逆转战胜[[哈茨足球俱乐部|哈茨]]的比赛中梅开二度。<ref name="BBC416">{{cite web |title=Celtic 3-1 Hearts: Patrick Roberts lauded after first goals |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35951200 |website=BBC Sport |access-date=2020-08-26 |date=2016-04-02 |language=en |archive-date=2022-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220425193543/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/35951200 }}</ref>在他打进三球的出色表现之后，罗伯茨被评为苏格兰四月份最佳球员。<ref>{{cite news|last=Pollard|first=Rob (6 May 2016)|title=Manchester City's Patrick Roberts wins Scottish Player of the Month award|url=http://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/patrick-roberts-manchester-city-celtic-11296606|access-date=2016-05-06|website=Manchester Evening|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220518074843/https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/patrick-roberts-manchester-city-celtic-11296606}}</ref>他在5月8日3-2击败[[阿伯丁足球俱乐部|阿伯丁]] 的比赛中梅开二度，帮助凯尔特人队夺得 [[苏格兰超级联赛|苏格兰超级联赛]] 冠军。<ref>{{cite news|last=Myson|first=Chris (8 May 2016)|title=Celtic 3–2 Aberdeen: Roberts double seals Scottish Premiership title|url=http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/2881/scottish-football/2016/05/08/23273402/celtic-3-2-aberdeen-roberts-double-seals-scottish|access-date=2016-05-08|website=Goal|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122013345/https://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/2881/scottish-football/2016/05/08/23273402/celtic-3-2-aberdeen-roberts-double-seals-scottish}}</ref> 

罗伯茨在2016年7月20日首次在[[欧洲冠军联賽|欧洲冠军联賽]]的比賽中上場，在3-0击败[[直布罗陀|直布罗陀]]的[[林肯紅魔鬼足球會|林肯紅魔鬼]]的比赛中首发并进球。 他之前拒绝了代表英格兰参加[[歐洲U-19足球錦標賽|歐洲U-19足球錦標賽]]的机会，以帮助凯尔特人晋级冠军联赛小組賽。<ref name="Lincoln Red Imps">{{cite web |title=Roberts happy to swerve England duty to help Celtic's European cause |url=https://news.stv.tv/sport/1361291-roberts-happy-to-swerve-england-duty-to-help-celtic-s-european-cause?amp |website=STV News |access-date=2020-08-26 |date=2016-07-21 |language=en |archive-date=2020-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826062820/https://news.stv.tv/sport/1361291-roberts-happy-to-swerve-england-duty-to-help-celtic-s-european-cause?amp }}</ref>2016年12月6日，罗伯茨打进了一個令人印象深刻的个人进球，并在与他的母队曼城的欧冠比赛中被评为最佳球员。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/38202631|title=Manchester City 1–1 Celtic|date=2016-12-06|publisher=BBC Sport|language=en|access-date=2022-01-22|archive-date=2017-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171207142417/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/38202631}}</ref>他在2016-17赛季代表凯尔特人上場43场比赛，踢進15个进球，帮助凯尔特人完成了一个不败的国内赛季，球隊连续第六次获得联赛冠军。

2017年8月28日，罗伯茨再一次外借凯尔特人队到賽季結束。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.celticfc.net/news/13158|title=Delight as Patrick Roberts rejoins Celtic on loan|date=2017-08-28|publisher=[[Celtic_F.C.|celticfc.net]]|language=en|access-date=2022-01-22|archive-date=2017-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170829032851/http://www.celticfc.net/news/13158}}</ref>在11月与[[马瑟韦尔足球俱乐部|马瑟韦尔]]的比赛中，罗伯茨腿筋受伤并缺阵数月。2018年3月18日，他在對陣马瑟韦尔的比赛中回歸賽場，在一場0-0平局中替补[[詹姆斯·福里斯特|詹姆斯·福里斯特]]上陣。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/11787/11306105/celtic-winger-patrick-roberts-refreshed-ahead-of-season-finale|title=Celtic winger Patrick Roberts refreshed ahead of season finale|publisher=Sky Sports|date=2018-03-27|access-date=2018-04-05|language=en|archive-date=2022-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122013343/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11787/11306105/celtic-winger-patrick-roberts-refreshed-ahead-of-season-finale}}</ref>

====赫罗纳(外借)====
罗伯茨在2018-19赛季租借到曼城的西班牙合作伙伴俱乐部[[吉羅納足球俱樂部|吉羅納]]，曼城表示，罗伯特发展的下一个阶段最理想是在世界上技术含量最高的联赛之一的西甲测试自己。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Pollard |first1=Rob |title=Patrick Roberts joins Girona on loan |url=https://www.mancity.com/news/first-team/first-team-news/2018/august/man-city-patrick-roberts-joins-girona-on-loan |publisher=Manchester City F.C. |access-date=2018-08-16 |language=en |archive-date=2022-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122125202/https://www.mancity.com/news/first-team/first-team-news/2018/august/man-city-patrick-roberts-joins-girona-on-loan }}</ref>在签约时，他是唯一一名参加西班牙顶级联赛的英格兰球员，第二天他在对阵皇家巴利亚多利德的比赛中替补出场。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/football/2018/aug/26/patrick-roberts-reaps-rewards-girona-manchester-city-connection|title=Patrick Roberts reaping rewards of Girona's complex City connection|work=The Guardian|last=Lowe|first=Sid|date=2018-08-26|access-date=2018-09-18|language=en|archive-date=2022-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220623210256/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2018/aug/26/patrick-roberts-reaps-rewards-girona-manchester-city-connection}}</ref>然而，他经历了一个不如意的赛季，[[吉羅納足球俱樂部|吉羅納]]降级到西乙，而他在19场上場的联赛中都未能進球。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.leicestermercury.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/who-reported-leicester-city-target-2903032|title=Who is reported Leicester City target Patrick Roberts? A profile on Manchester City youngster|publisher=Leicestershire Live|last=Kemble|first=Jamie|date=2019-05-24|access-date=2019-05-24|language=en|archive-date=2022-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220516131458/https://www.leicestermercury.co.uk/sport/football/transfer-news/who-reported-leicester-city-target-2903032}}</ref>

====诺里奇城(外借)====
2019年5月30日，英冠冠軍, 來季升上英超聯賽的[[诺里奇城足球俱乐部|诺里奇城]]与罗伯茨签订了为期一个赛季的租借协议。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/48465832/|title=Patrick Roberts: Manchester City midfielder joins Norwich on season-long loan|website=bbc|language=en-gb|date=2019-05-30|access-date=2022-01-22|archive-date=2022-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220514003219/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/48465832}}</ref>然而罗伯茨只上場4次的程況下，诺里奇城宣佈租借提早終結。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.canaries.co.uk/content/roberts-norwich-loan-deal-ends|title=Roberts’ Norwich loan deal ends|website=canaries.co.uk|language=en-gb|date=|access-date=2022-01-22|archive-date=2022-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122125154/https://www.canaries.co.uk/content/roberts-norwich-loan-deal-ends}}</ref>

====米德尔斯堡(外借)====
2020年1月2日，罗伯茨租借加盟[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米德尔斯堡]]直到[[2019年至2020年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2019–20赛季]]结束。<ref>{{Cite news |url = https://www.mfc.co.uk/news/patrick-roberts-joins-boro-on-loan |title = Patrick Roberts Joins Boro On Loan |publisher = Middlesbrough F.C. |date = 2020-01-02 |access-date = 2020-10-12 |language = en |archive-date = 2022-01-22 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220122125200/https://www.mfc.co.uk/news/patrick-roberts-joins-boro-on-loan }}</ref> 他在2020年 7月14日米德尔斯堡2-1击败[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]的比赛中打进了他在米德尔斯堡的首个进球。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hartlepoolmail.co.uk/sport/football/middlesbrough-fc/statistics-behind-patrick-roberts-reading-display-after-manchester-city-nets-first-goal-middlesbrough-2915865 |title=The statistics behind Patrick Roberts' Reading display after Manchester City loanee nets first goal for Middlesbrough |date=2020-07-14|publisher=hartlepoolmail.co.uk |access-date=2021-01-03}}</ref> 2020年10月12日，曼城宣布罗伯茨將會在[[2020年至2021年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2019–20赛季]]繼續租借到[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米德尔斯堡]]。<ref>{{Cite news |url = https://www.mfc.co.uk/news/patrick-roberts-rejoins-boro-on-loan |title = Patrick Roberts Rejoins Boro On Loan |publisher = Middlesbrough F.C. |date = 12 October 2020 |access-date = 12 October 2020 |language = en |archive-date = 2022-01-22 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220122125221/https://www.mfc.co.uk/news/patrick-roberts-rejoins-boro-on-loan }}</ref>

====德比郡(外借)====
2021年2月1日，罗伯茨將會在[[2020年至2021年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2019–20赛季]]的餘下日子租借加盟[[德比郡足球俱乐部|德比郡]]。<ref>{{cite news |title=RAMS MOVE TO SIGN WINGER ROBERTS |url=https://www.dcfc.co.uk/news/2021/02/rams-move-to-sign-winger-roberts |access-date=2021-02-01 |work=Derby County F.C. |date=2021-02-01 |language=en |archive-date=2022-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122125205/https://www.dcfc.co.uk/news/2021/02/rams-move-to-sign-winger-roberts }}</ref>两天后，他在联赛客场0-3负于[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|罗瑟勒姆]]的比赛中首次代表德比郡出场。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/55920060 |title=Preston North End 1-2 Rotherham United: Late Millers flourish leave Rooney's Rams reeling |website=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |date=2021-02-03 |accessdate=2021-02-15 |language=en |archive-date=2022-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220517044257/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/55920060 }}</ref>

